## Index Stratejisi
```
Karar Agaci:
├── WHERE'de sik kullanilan kolon? -> Non-clustered index
├── WHERE + ORDER BY birlikte? -> Composite index (WHERE kolonlari once)
├── SELECT'te az kolon? -> Covering index (INCLUDE)
├── Cok sayida duplicate? -> Filtered index (WHERE IsActive = 1)
├── Text arama? -> Full-text index
├── JSON property? -> Computed column + index
├── Buyuk tablo (100M+)? -> Partitioned index

KURALLAR:
- TenantId HER composite index'in ILK kolonunda olmali
- Max 5-6 index per table (write performance)
- Kullanilmayan index'leri tespit et: sys.dm_db_index_usage_stats
- Index rebuild: fragmentation > %30
```

## Partitioning Karar Agaci
```
├── Tablo 50M+ row mu? -> Partition degerlendir
├── Date-based query pattern? -> RANGE RIGHT on date column
├── Tenant-based isolation? -> TenantId ile partition
├── Archive gerekliligi? -> Partition switch ile hizli archive
├── Yoksa -> Partition EKLEME (overhead)
```

## Query Optimization

### EF Core Query Stratejisi
```
├── Read-only sorgu? -> AsNoTracking() ZORUNLU
├── Liste/grid? -> Select projection (sadece gerekli alanlar)
├── Pagination? -> Keyset pagination (OFFSET-FETCH DEGIL)
├── Bulk read? -> SplitQuery (cart. explosion onleme)
├── Bulk write? -> ExecuteUpdate/ExecuteDelete (EF Core 7+)
├── Rapor/aggregation? -> Raw SQL veya view
├── Sik calisan sorgu? -> Compiled query
```

### Keyset Pagination (OFFSET-FETCH'ten ustun)
```csharp
// DOGRU: Keyset — O(1) her sayfada
var items = await _context.Items
    .AsNoTracking()
    .Where(x => x.TenantId == tenantId)
    .Where(x => x.Id > lastSeenId) // cursor
    .OrderBy(x => x.Id)
    .Take(pageSize)
    .Select(x => new ItemDto { Id = x.Id, Name = x.Name })
    .ToListAsync(ct);

// YANLIS: OFFSET — buyuk tablolarda yavas
// .Skip((page - 1) * pageSize).Take(pageSize)
```

### Compiled Query
```csharp
private static readonly Func<AppDbContext, Guid, Guid, CancellationToken, Task<Order?>>
    GetOrderById = EF.CompileAsyncQuery(
        (AppDbContext ctx, Guid tenantId, Guid orderId, CancellationToken ct) =>
            ctx.Orders.AsNoTracking()
                .FirstOrDefault(o => o.TenantId == tenantId && o.Id == orderId));
```

## Multi-Tenancy DB Kurallari
- Her entity: `TenantId` (Guid) ZORUNLU
- Global query filter: `builder.HasQueryFilter(x => x.TenantId == _tid)`
- Row-Level Security (RLS): SQL Server native alternatif
- Connection pool: tenant basina pool DEGIL, shared pool
- ASLA IgnoreQueryFilters (super admin + audit haric)
- ASLA cross-tenant JOIN
- TEST: her integration test cross-tenant erisim denemesi + basarisiz olmali

## Temporal Tables (Audit Trail)
```sql
ALTER TABLE Orders ADD
    ValidFrom DATETIME2 GENERATED ALWAYS AS ROW START,
    ValidTo DATETIME2 GENERATED ALWAYS AS ROW END,
    PERIOD FOR SYSTEM_TIME (ValidFrom, ValidTo);
ALTER TABLE Orders SET (SYSTEM_VERSIONING = ON);
```

## Migration Stratejisi
- Her migration tek sorumluluk (table create, index add, data migration AYRI)
- Idempotent migration: `IF NOT EXISTS` kontrol
- Data migration: ayri migration dosyasi
- Rollback plani: Down() her zaman yazilmali
- Production: ONLINE index, minimal lock

## Deadlock Onleme
```
1. Tablolara erisim AYNI SIRADA (ORDER BY table name)
2. Transaction sure: < 2 saniye
3. UPDLOCK + ROWLOCK hint (gerektiginde)
4. Isolation: READ COMMITTED SNAPSHOT (RCSI) ON
5. Retry logic: deadlock exception catch + 3 retry
```

## Connection Pool Tuning
```
Min Pool Size=10;Max Pool Size=100;Connection Timeout=15;
Command Timeout=30;Encrypt=True;TrustServerCertificate=False;
MultipleActiveResultSets=False;
```

## Anti-Pattern'ler
| Anti-Pattern | Dogru Yaklasim |
|---|---|
| Migration adlandirma tutarsiz | `YYYYMMDDHHMM_DescriptiveName` (EF convention) |
| Global query filter unutma | Her tenant entity'de `HasQueryFilter(x => x.TenantId == _tid)` |
| TenantId index eksik | Composite index'te TenantId ILK kolon; sorgu filter ile uyumlu |
| OFFSET pagination buyuk tabloda | Cursor/keyset pagination (Id > lastSeenId) |
| N+1 sorgu | Include / projection / batch query |
| Migration'da breaking schema degisiklik | Ayri migration; veri donusumu ayri adim |
| DateTime.Now / local time | UTC sakla; sunucu timezone bagimsiz |

